Defendant in custody.    
Defendant is before the Court for sentencing his probation having been revoked effective 10-26-17.   
Defendant is sentenced to the Wisconsin State Prison System for a total sentence of eight (8) years.   Four (4) years initial confinement, followed by four (4) years extended supervision.   Conditions of extended supervision are:
1) Pay restitution of $866.05 to Manitowoc Heating and Refrigeration, c/o Terry Welnicke, 211 N. 10th Street, Manitowoc, WI.  
2) Maintain full-time employment/schooling combination; 
3) Assessment/treatment/counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process; 
4) Have no contact with Manitowoc Heating and Refrigeration; 
5) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same; 
6) Obtain mental health assessment and follow through; 
7) Pay costs of action; 
8) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC. 
Court finds the defendant is eligible for the Challenge Incarceration Program and the Substance Abuse Program.   
Defendant is entitled to 315 days sentence credit.   
